This is a placeholder for the buzzer.mp3 sound file.

To complete the implementation of the game:
1. Replace this placeholder with an actual buzzer.mp3 sound file (1-2 seconds long)
2. You can find free sound files from sources like Freesound.org
3. Make sure the file is named exactly "buzzer.mp3" and is in this directory
4. The file should be small (under 100KB) for optimal performance
5. The buzzer should be distinct from the beep sound and more attention-grabbing

Without this sound file, the game's end-of-timer functionality will not work properly.